title: Dak Prescott, Myles Garrett, Jamal Adams, NBA bubble, NCAAFB
itunes:title: Dak Prescott, Myles Garrett, Jamal Adams, NBA bubble, NCAAFB
description:
Colin explains why Dak Prescott isn't getting the contract he wants, the Browns extending Myles Garrett, the Jets not spending to keep Jamal Adams, the snitch line for the NBA bubble, and the possibility of college players opting to not play if there is a Spring season. Guests include Nick Wright, Howard Beck, Clarence Hill, and Dave Wannstedt.
